<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>Bestresto - 로그인 </title>

    <base href="/">
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">


    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        *{
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body{
            background: rgb(219,226,226);
        }
        .row{
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 12px 12px 22px grey;
        }
        img{
            border-top-left-radius: 30px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 30px;
        }
        .btn1{
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            height: 50px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn1:hover{
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid;
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<section class="Form my-4 mx-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <img src="#" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 px-5 pt-5 ">
                <h1>Bestresto</h1>
                <h4>로그인</h4>
                <form>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-7">
                            <input type="email" placeholder="youremail@email.com" class="form-control my-3  p-4">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-7">
                            <input type="password" placeholder="********" class="form-control">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col-lg-7">
                            <button type="button" class="btn1 mt-3 mb-5 " id="btn-login">로그인</button>
                       </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#">비밀번호를 잊어버렸습니다</a>
                    <p>아직 계정이 없나요? <a href="/user-sign-in">회원가입하기</a></p>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

